Now, let's simplify this linear equation to make it easier to solve. We group the $t$ and $u$ terms on the left side:

$$
\begin{aligned}
10t + u &= 10u + t + 45 \\
10t - t + u - 10u &= 45 \\
9t - 9u &= 45 \\
t - u &= 5 \quad \text{(Equation 1)}
\end{aligned}
$$
